leve.name: From Creepers to Squatters
leve.description: The Temple Knights are considering establishing a checkpoint in the Churning Mists, but wish to know more about the foreign landscape. A suitable area must have its share of hills and craggy outcrops to provide a watchtower with ample cover, yet flat enough to provide a stable foundation. The Congregation seeks to commission one capable of conducting a geological survey and bringing soil samples for use in drafting new maps.
leve.client: Temple Knights Second Commander Ser Handeloup
